    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='216:243'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-1a' );" name="005-1a" class="pb">[005-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='243:260'>監本纂圖重言重意互註尚書卷第五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='260:274'>盤庚上第九　商書　孔氏傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='274:313'>盤庚五遷將治亳殷<span class='krp-note'>自湯至盤庚凡五遷都盤庚治亳/殷盤本又作般歩干反治直吏反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='313:351'>民咨胥怨<span class='krp-note'>胥相也民不欲徙乃咨嗟憂愁相/與怨上胥徐思餘反怨紆萬反</span>作盤庚三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='351:399'>篇盤庚<span class='krp-note'>盤庚殷王名殷質以名篇馬云祖乙曾孫祖丁之子/不言盤庚誥何非但録其誥也取其徙而立功故以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='399:439'><span class='krp-note'>盤庚/名篇</span>盤庚遷于殷<span class='krp-note'>亳之/别名</span>民不適有居<span class='krp-note'>適之也不欲/之殷有邑居</span>率</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='439:475'>籲衆慼岀矢言<span class='krp-note'>籲和也率和衆憂之人出正/直之言籲音喻慼千歷反</span>曰我王來</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='475:512'>旣爰宅于兹<span class='krp-note'>我王祖乙居耿爰於/也言祖乙巳居於此</span>重我民無盡劉<span class='krp-note'>劉/殺</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='512:545'><span class='krp-note'>也所以遷此重我民無/欲盡殺故盡子忍反</span>不能胥匡以生卜稽曰其如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='545:595'>台<span class='krp-note'>言民不能相匡以生則當卜考于龜以/徙曰其如我所行稽工兮反台音怡</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>其如台二本/篇髙宗肜日</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='595:622'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-1b' );" name="005-1b" class="pb">[005-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='622:664'>重意<span class='krp-note'>卜稽曰其如台湯誓夏罪其如台髙宗肜/日乃曰其如台西伯戡黎今王其如台</span>先王有服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='664:702'>恪謹天命兹猶不常寜<span class='krp-note'>先王有所服行敬謹天命如此/尚不常安有可遷輒遷恪苦各</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='702:742'><span class='krp-note'>反</span>不常厥邑于今五邦<span class='krp-note'>湯遷亳仲丁遷嚻河亶甲居相/祖乙居耿我往居亳凡五徙國</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='742:778'><span class='krp-note'>都馬云五邦謂商/丘亳嚻相耿也</span>今不承于古罔知天之斷命<span class='krp-note'>今不/承古</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='778:818'><span class='krp-note'>而徙是無知天將斷/絶汝命斷又音短</span>矧曰其克從先王之烈<span class='krp-note'>天將絶命/尚無知之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='818:861'><span class='krp-note'>兄能從先王之/業乎從才容反</span>若顚木之有由蘗<span class='krp-note'>言今往遷都更求昌/盛如顚仆之木有用</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='861:900'><span class='krp-note'>生蘖哉蘖五逹反本又作枿馬云顚/木而肄生曰枿仆音赴又步北反</span>天其永我命于兹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='900:932'>新邑<span class='krp-note'>言天其長我命於/此新邑不可不徙</span>紹復先王之大業底綏四方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='932:971'><span class='krp-note'>言我徙欲如/此厎之履反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>厎綏四方泰/誓寵綏四方</span>盤庚斆于民由乃在位</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='971:1011'>以常舊服正法度<span class='krp-note'>斆教也教人使用汝在位之命用常/故事正其法度斆戸教反下如字度</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='1011:1038'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-2a' );" name="005-2a" class="pb">[005-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='1038:1078'><span class='krp-note'>如/字</span>曰無或敢伏小人之攸箴<span class='krp-note'>言無有敢伏絶小人之所/欲箴規上者戒朝臣箴音</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='1078:1113'><span class='krp-note'>之林反馬云諫/也朝直遥反</span>王命衆悉至于庭<span class='krp-note'>衆羣臣/以下</span>王若曰格</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='1113:1143'>汝衆予告汝訓<span class='krp-note'>告汝以/法教</span>汝猷黜乃心無傲從康<span class='krp-note'>謀/退</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='1143:1176'><span class='krp-note'>汝違上之心無傲慢從/心所安傲鄭五報反</span>古我先王亦惟圖任舊人共</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='1176:1227'>政<span class='krp-note'>先王謀任乆老成人/共治其政任而鴆反</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>古我先王三本篇/二盤庚下篇一</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>亦惟圖/任舊人</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='1227:1268'><span class='krp-note'>共政大誥/爾惟舊人</span>王播告之修不匿厥指<span class='krp-note'>王布告人以所修之/政不匿其指播波餓</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='1268:1303'><span class='krp-note'>反匿女/力反</span>王用丕欽罔有逸言民用丕變<span class='krp-note'>王用大敬其/政教無有逸</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='1303:1331'><span class='krp-note'>豫之言民用/大變從化</span>今汝聒聒起信險膚子弗知乃所訟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='1331:1378'><span class='krp-note'>聒聒無知之貌起信險僞膚受之言我不知汝所訟/言何謂聒故活反馬及說文皆云拒善自用之意</span>非予自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='1378:1405'>荒兹德惟汝含德不惕予一人予若觀火<span class='krp-note'>我之欲/徙非廢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='1405:1432'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-2b' );" name="005-2b" class="pb">[005-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1432:1472'><span class='krp-note'>此德汝不從我命所含惡德但不畏/懼我耳我視汝情如視火惕他歷反</span>予亦拙謀作乃逸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1472:1507'><span class='krp-note'>逸過也我不威脅汝徙是/我拙謀成汝過拙之劣反</span>若網在綱有條而不紊若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1507:1545'>農服田力穡乃亦有秋<span class='krp-note'>紊亂也穡耕稼也下之順上當/如網在綱各有條理而不亂也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1545:1579'><span class='krp-note'>農勤穡則有秋下承上/則有福紊音問徐音文</span>汝克黜乃心施實德于民至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1579:1612'>于㛰友丕乃敢大言汝有積德<span class='krp-note'>汝羣臣能退汝違上/之心施實德於民至</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1612:1645'><span class='krp-note'>于㛰姻僚友則我大乃/敢言汝有積德之臣</span>乃不畏戎毒于逺邇惰農自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1645:1673'>安不昬作勞不服田畒越其罔有黍稷<span class='krp-note'>戎大昬強/越於也言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1673:1726'><span class='krp-note'>不欲徙則是不畏大毒於逺近如怠惰之農苟自安逸不強作/勞於田畒則黍稷無所有昬馬同本或作暋音敏爾雅昬暋皆</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1726:1760'><span class='krp-note'>訓強故兩存越本又作/粤音曰于也強其丈反</span>汝不和吉言于百姓惟汝自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1760:1792'>生毒<span class='krp-note'>責公卿不能和喻/百官是自生毒害</span>乃敗禍姦宄以自災于厥身</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1792:1819'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-3a' );" name="005-3a" class="pb">[005-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1819:1846'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-4a' );" name="005-4a" class="pb">[005-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1846:1884'>予有咎<span class='krp-note'>我刑戮汝非我咎也靖謀也是/汝自爲非謀所致馬云靖安也</span>遲任有言曰人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1884:1922'>惟求舊器非求舊惟新<span class='krp-note'>遲任古賢言人貴舊器貴新汝/不徙是不貴舊遟直疑反徐待</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1922:1953'><span class='krp-note'>夷反任而今反/馬云古老成人</span>古我先王曁乃祖乃父胥及逸勤予</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1953:1998'>敢動用非罰<span class='krp-note'>言古之君臣相與同勞逸子孫所冝/法之我豈敢動用非常之罰脅汝乎</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>古/我</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1998:2037'><span class='krp-note'>先王三本篇/二盤庚下一</span>丗選爾勞予不掩爾善<span class='krp-note'>選數也言我丗/丗數汝功勤丕</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='2037:2076'><span class='krp-note'>掩蔽汝善是我忠於汝選息轉反/又思管反掩本又作弇數色主反</span>兹予大享于先王爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='2076:2117'>祖其從與享之<span class='krp-note'>古者天子録功臣配食於廟大享烝甞/也所以不掩汝善與音預烝之承反</span>作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='2117:2151'>福作災予亦不敢動用非德<span class='krp-note'>善自作福惡自作災我/不敢動用非罰加汝非</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='2151:2188'><span class='krp-note'>德賞汝乎從汝/善惡而報之</span>予告汝于難若射之有志<span class='krp-note'>告汝行事/之難當如</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='2188:2225'><span class='krp-note'>射之有所凖志必中所志乃善/射食夜反凖音准中丁仲反</span>汝無侮老成人無弱孤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='2225:2252'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-4b' );" name="005-4b" class="pb">[005-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='2252:2293'>有㓜<span class='krp-note'>不用老成人之言是侮老之不徙則孤/㓜受害是弱易之侮亡甫反易以䜴反</span>各長于厥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='2293:2326'>居勉出乃力聽予一人之作猷<span class='krp-note'>盤庚勑臣下各思長/於其居勉盡心出力</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='2326:2355'><span class='krp-note'>聽從遷徙之/謀長丁丈反</span>無有逺邇用罪伐厥死用德彰厥善</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='2355:2414'><span class='krp-note'>言逺近待之如一罪以懲之使勿犯伐去其/死道德以明之使勸慕競爲善去起吕反</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>無有逺邇二/本篇旅<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0729' title='KR0729' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0729.png'/></span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='2414:2445'>邦之臧惟汝衆<span class='krp-note'>有善則衆臣之/功臧徐子郎反</span>邦之不臧惟予一人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='2445:2485'>有佚罰<span class='krp-note'>佚失也是己失政之/罰罪已之義佚音逸</span>凡爾衆其惟致告<span class='krp-note'>致我誠/告汝衆</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='2485:2510'>自今至于後日各恭爾事齊乃位度乃口<span class='krp-note'>奉其/職事</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='2510:2553'><span class='krp-note'>正齊其位以法度居汝口/勿浮言度徐如字亦作渡</span>罰及爾身弗可悔<span class='krp-note'>不從我謀/罰及汝身</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='2553:2563'><span class='krp-note'>雖悔可/及乎</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='2563:2577'>盤庚中第十　商書　孔氏傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='2577:2604'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-5a' );" name="005-5a" class="pb">[005-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='2604:2633'>盤庚作惟渉河以民遷<span class='krp-note'>爲此南渡河/之法用民徙</span>乃話民之弗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='2633:2672'>率誕告用亶其有衆<span class='krp-note'>話善言民不循教發善言大告用/誠於衆話胡快反馬云告也言也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='2672:2715'><span class='krp-note'>誕徐音但亶丁但反/馬本作單音同誠也</span>咸造勿䙝在王庭<span class='krp-note'>造至也衆皆至/王庭無䙝慢造</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='2715:2753'><span class='krp-note'>十報反注同馬在早/反云爲也䙝息列反</span>盤庚乃登進厥民<span class='krp-note'>升進命/使前</span>曰明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='2753:2793'>聽朕言無荒失朕命<span class='krp-note'>荒/廢</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>明聽朕言湯誓悉聽朕言/泰誓咸聽朕言吕刑皆聽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='2793:2827'><span class='krp-note'>朕/言</span>嗚呼古我前后罔不惟民之承<span class='krp-note'>言我先丗賢君/無不承安民而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='2827:2866'><span class='krp-note'>恤/之</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>古我前后本篇古我先/后上篇下篇古我先王</span>保后胥慼鮮以不浮于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='2866:2909'>天時<span class='krp-note'>民亦安君之政相與憂行君令浮行也少/以不行於天時者言皆行天時鮮息淺反</span>殷降大虐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='2909:2943'>先王不懷<span class='krp-note'>我殷家於天降大災則/先王不思故居而行徙</span>厥攸作視民利用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='2943:2981'>遷<span class='krp-note'>其所爲視民/有利則用徙</span>汝曷弗念我古后之聞<span class='krp-note'>古后先王之/聞謂遷事曷</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='2981:3008'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-5b' );" name="005-5b" class="pb">[005-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='3008:3038'><span class='krp-note'>何末反/下同</span>承汝俾汝惟喜康共非汝有咎比于罰<span class='krp-note'>今/我</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='3038:3091'><span class='krp-note'>法先王惟民之承故承汝使汝徙惟與汝其喜安非謂汝有惡/徙汝令比近於殃罰俾必爾反咎其九反比毗志反徐扶志反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='3091:3124'><span class='krp-note'>注及下同共羣用反令/力呈反近附近之近</span>予若籲懷兹新邑亦惟汝故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='3124:3162'>以丕從厥志<span class='krp-note'>言我順和懷此新邑欲利汝衆/故大從其志而徙之籲羊戍反</span>今予將試</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='3162:3196'>以汝遷安定厥邦<span class='krp-note'>試/用</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>今予將試以汝/遷二並本篇</span>汝不憂朕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='3196:3223'>心之攸困<span class='krp-note'>所困不/順上命</span>乃咸大不宣乃心欽念以忱動</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='3223:3260'>予一人<span class='krp-note'>汝皆大不布腹心敬念以誠感/動我是汝不盡忠忱市林反</span>爾惟自鞠自苦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='3260:3298'><span class='krp-note'>鞠窮也言汝爲臣不忠/自取窮苦鞠居六反</span>若乗舟汝弗濟臭厥載<span class='krp-note'>言不/徙之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='3298:3337'><span class='krp-note'>害如舟在水中流不渡臭敗其所載/物臭徐尺售反載如字又在代反</span>爾忱不屬惟胥以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='3337:3375'>沈不其或稽自怒曷瘳<span class='krp-note'>汝忠誠不屬逮古苟不欲徙相/與沈溺不考之先王禍至自怒</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='3375:3402'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-6a' );" name="005-6a" class="pb">[005-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='3402:3438'><span class='krp-note'>何瘳瘥乎屬音燭注同馬云/獨也沈直林反瘳勑留反</span>汝不謀長以思乃災汝誕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='3438:3475'>勸憂<span class='krp-note'>汝不謀長乆之計思汝不徙之/災苟不欲徙是大勸憂之道</span>今其有今罔後汝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='3475:3509'>何生在上<span class='krp-note'>言不徙無後計汝何得/乆生在人上禍將及汝</span>今予命汝一無起</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='3509:3541'>穢以自臭<span class='krp-note'>我一心命汝汝違我/是自臭敗穢於廢反</span>恐人倚乃身迂乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='3541:3582'>心<span class='krp-note'>言汝旣不欲徙又爲他人所誤倚曲迂僻/倚於綺反徐於竒反迂音于僻匹亦反</span>予迓續乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='3582:3615'>命于天予豈汝威用奉畜汝衆<span class='krp-note'>迓迎也言我徙欲迎/續汝命于天豈以威</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='3615:3652'><span class='krp-note'>脅汝乎用奉畜養汝衆迓五駕/反畜許竹反下同脅虚業反</span>予念我先神后之勞爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='3652:3687'>先予丕克羞爾用懷爾然<span class='krp-note'>言我亦法湯大能進勞汝/以義懷汝心而汝違我是</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='3687:3718'><span class='krp-note'>汝反先人勞力報/反又如字注同</span>失于政陳于兹髙后丕乃崇降罪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='3718:3761'>疾曰曷虐朕民<span class='krp-note'>崇重也今旣失政而陳乆於此而不徙湯/必大重下罪疾於我曰何爲虐我民而不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='3761:3788'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-6b' );" name="005-6b" class="pb">[005-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='3788:3822'><span class='krp-note'>徙乎重直勇/反又直恭反</span>汝萬民乃不生生曁予一人猷同心<span class='krp-note'>不/進</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='3822:3848'><span class='krp-note'>進謀同/心徙</span>先后丕降與汝罪疾曰曷不曁朕㓜孫有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='3848:3882'>比<span class='krp-note'>言非但罪我亦將罪汝/㓜孫盤庚自謂比同心</span>故有爽德自上其罰汝汝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='3882:3916'>罔能迪<span class='krp-note'>湯有明德在天見汝情下/罰汝汝無能道言無辭</span>古我先后旣勞乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='3916:3951'>祖乃父<span class='krp-note'>勞之共/治人</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>古我先后篇/首古我前后</span>汝共作我畜民汝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='3951:3996'>有戕則在乃心<span class='krp-note'>戕殘也汝共我治民有殘人之心而不欲徙/是反父祖之行戕在良反又七良反行下孟</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='3996:4018'><span class='krp-note'>反</span>我先后綏乃祖乃父乃祖乃父乃斷棄汝不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='4018:4066'>救乃死<span class='krp-note'>言我先王安汝父祖之忠今汝不忠汝父/祖必斷絶棄汝命不救汝死斷丁緩反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>乃祖/乃父</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='4066:4102'><span class='krp-note'>君牙惟乃/祖乃父</span>兹予有亂政同位具乃貝玉<span class='krp-note'>亂治也此我/有治政之臣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='4102:4141'><span class='krp-note'>同位於父祖不念盡忠但念貝玉/而巳言其貪洽直吏反盡子忍反</span>乃祖乃父丕乃告我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='4141:4168'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-7a' );" name="005-7a" class="pb">[005-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='4168:4206'>髙后曰作丕刑于朕孫<span class='krp-note'>言汝父祖見汝貪而不忠必大/乃告湯曰作大刑於我子孫求</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='4206:4245'><span class='krp-note'>討不忠之罪乃告工號反/我髙后本又作乃祖乃父</span>迪髙后丕乃崇降弗祥<span class='krp-note'>言/汝</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='4245:4286'><span class='krp-note'>父祖開道湯大重下不善以/罰汝陳忠孝之義以督之</span>嗚呼今予告汝不易<span class='krp-note'>凡所/言皆</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='4286:4328'><span class='krp-note'>不易之事易/以䜴反注同</span>永敬大恤無胥絶逺<span class='krp-note'>長敬我言大憂行之/無相與絶逺棄廢之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='4328:4360'><span class='krp-note'>逺干萬反又/如字注同</span>汝分猷念以相從各設中于乃心<span class='krp-note'>羣/臣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='4360:4406'><span class='krp-note'>當分明相與謀念和以相從各設中/正於汝心汝分扶問反又如字注同</span>乃有不吉不迪<span class='krp-note'>不善/不道</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='4406:4447'><span class='krp-note'>謂凶/人</span>顚越不恭暫遇姦宄<span class='krp-note'>顚隕越墜也不恭不奉上命/暫遇人而刼奪之爲姦於外</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='4447:4475'><span class='krp-note'>爲宄於内/隕于敏反</span>我乃劓殄滅之無遺育無俾易種于兹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='4475:4524'>新邑<span class='krp-note'>劓割育長也言不吉之人當割絶滅之無遺長其類無/使易種於此新邑劓魚器反徐吾氣反殄徒典反易如</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='4524:4577'><span class='krp-note'>字又以䜴反注同長/丁丈反下遺長同</span>互註<span class='krp-note'>左哀十一年呉將伐齊越子率其衆/以朝焉子胥諌曰越在我心腹之疾</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='4577:4604'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-7b' );" name="005-7b" class="pb">[005-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='4604:4657'><span class='krp-note'>也壤地同而有欲於我夫其柔服求儕其欲也不如早從事焉/得志於齊猶獲石田也無所用之越不爲沼呉其泯矣使醫除</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='4657:4710'><span class='krp-note'>疾而曰不遺類焉者未之有也盤庚之誥曰其有顚越不共則/劓殄無遺育無俾易種于兹新邑是商所以興也今君易之將</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='4710:4738'><span class='krp-note'>以求大不亦/難乎弗聽</span>往哉生生今予將試以汝遷永建乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='4738:4789'>家<span class='krp-note'>自今巳往進進於善我用以/汝徙長立汝家卿大夫稱家</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>往哉七舜典二本篇微/子之命康誥畢命文侯</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='4789:4810'><span class='krp-note'>之命各一〇今予將/試以汝遷二並本篇</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='4810:4825'>盤庚下第十一　商書　孔氏傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='4825:4858'>盤庚旣遷奠厥攸居乃正厥位<span class='krp-note'>定其所居正郊廟朝/社之位奠田薦反朝</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='4858:4893'><span class='krp-note'>直遥/反</span>綏爰有衆曰無戲怠懋建大命<span class='krp-note'>安於有衆戒無/戲怠勉立大教</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='4893:4918'>今予其敷心腹腎腸歷告爾百姓于朕志<span class='krp-note'>布心/腹言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='4918:4951'><span class='krp-note'>輸誠於百官以告志腎/時忍反腸徐持良反</span>罔罪爾衆爾無共怒恊比讒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='4951:4978'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-8a' );" name="005-8a" class="pb">[005-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='4978:5023'>言予一人<span class='krp-note'>羣臣前有此過故禁其後今我不罪汝汝勿共/怒我合比凶人而妄言比毗志反讒仕咸反</span>古</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='5023:5062'>我先王將多于前功<span class='krp-note'>言以遷徙多大/前人之功美</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>古我先王上/篇古我前后</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='5062:5096'><span class='krp-note'>又古我/先后</span>適于山用降我凶德嘉績于朕邦<span class='krp-note'>徙必依山/之險無城</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='5096:5135'><span class='krp-note'>郭之勞下去凶惡之德立善功於我/國降工巷反徐下江反去羌吕反</span>今我民用蕩析離</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='5135:5179'>居罔有定極<span class='krp-note'>水泉沈溺故蕩析離居無安定之/極徙以爲之極析先歷反注同</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>今我/民又</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='5179:5212'><span class='krp-note'>西伯/戡黎</span>爾謂朕曷震動萬民以遷<span class='krp-note'>言皆不眀/巳本心</span>肆上帝將</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='5212:5245'>復我髙祖之德亂越我家<span class='krp-note'>以徙故天將復湯德治/理於我家治直吏反</span>朕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='5245:5277'>及篤敬恭承民命用永地于新邑<span class='krp-note'>言我當與厚敬之/臣奉承民命用長</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='5277:5315'><span class='krp-note'>居新/邑</span>肆予冲人非廢厥謀弔由靈<span class='krp-note'>冲童童人謙也弔至/靈善也非廢謂動謀</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='5315:5354'><span class='krp-note'>於衆至用其善/弔音的或如字</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>肆予冲人/重見大誥</span>各非敢違卜用宏兹賁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='5354:5381'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-8b' );" name="005-8b" class="pb">[005-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='5381:5419'><span class='krp-note'>宏賁皆大也君臣用謀不敢違/卜用大此遷都大業賁扶云反</span>嗚呼邦伯師長百執事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='5419:5461'>之人尚皆隱哉<span class='krp-note'>國伯二伯及州牧也衆長公卿也言當/庶幾相隱括共爲善政長丁丈反注同</span>予</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='5461:5495'>其懋簡相爾念敬我衆<span class='krp-note'>簡大相助也勉大助汝/念敬我衆民相息亮反</span>朕不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='5495:5522'>肩好貨敢恭生生鞠人謀人之保居叙欽<span class='krp-note'>肩任也/我不任</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='5522:5568'><span class='krp-note'>貪貨之人敢奉用進進於善者人之窮困能謀安/其居者則我式叙而敬之好呼報反任而林反</span>今我旣羞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='5568:5604'>告爾于朕志若否罔有弗欽<span class='krp-note'>巳進告汝之後順於汝心/與否當以情告我無敢有</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='5604:5646'><span class='krp-note'>不敬告/故報反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>罔有弗欽冏/命罔有不欽</span>無緫于貨寳生生自庸<span class='krp-note'>無緫/貨寳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='5646:5688'><span class='krp-note'>以求位當進進/皆自用功德</span>式敷民德永肩一心<span class='krp-note'>用布示民必以德義/長任一心以事君</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='5688:5703'>說命上第十二　商書　孔氏傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='5703:5747'>髙宗夢得說<span class='krp-note'>盤庚弟小乙子名武丁德髙可尊故號髙宗/夢得賢相其名曰說說本又作兊音恱注及</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='5747:5774'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-9a' );" name="005-9a" class="pb">[005-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='5774:5807'>九有之師爰革夏正<span class='krp-note'>爰於也於得九有之衆/遂伐夏勝之改其正</span>非天私</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='5807:5845'>我有商惟天佑于一德<span class='krp-note'>非天私商而王之佑助一德所/以王而王于况反下同或如字</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='5845:5875'>非商求于下民惟民歸于一德<span class='krp-note'>非商以力求民/民自歸于一德</span>德</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='5875:5900'>惟一動罔不吉德二三動罔不凶<span class='krp-note'>二三言/不一</span>惟吉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='5900:5933'>凶不僭在人惟天降災祥在德<span class='krp-note'>行善則吉行惡則凶/是不差德一天降之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='5933:5970'><span class='krp-note'>善不一天降之災/是在德僭子念反</span>今嗣王新服厥命惟新厥德<span class='krp-note'>其命/王命</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='5970:6012'><span class='krp-note'>新其德/戒勿怠</span>終始惟一時乃日新<span class='krp-note'>言德行終始不衰殺是乃/日新之義行下孟反殺色</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='6012:6053'><span class='krp-note'>界反衰微也殺害/也言小小害也</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>時乃日新仲虺/之誥德日新</span>任官惟賢材左右</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='6053:6102'>惟其人<span class='krp-note'>官賢材而任之非賢材不可任/選左右必忠良不忠良非其人</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>任官惟賢材武/成建官惟賢〇</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='6102:6143'><span class='krp-note'>左右惟其人周官/官不必備惟其人</span>臣爲上爲德爲下爲民<span class='krp-note'>言臣奉上布/德順下訓民</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='6143:6170'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-9b' );" name="005-9b" class="pb">[005-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='6170:6212'><span class='krp-note'>不可官所私任非其人爲上于僞反下爲/民同爲德如字下爲下同徐皆于僞反</span>其難其愼惟和</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='6212:6262'>惟一<span class='krp-note'>其難無以爲易其愼無以輕之羣臣/當和一心以事君政乃善易以䜴反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>惟和惟一禹/謨惟精惟一</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='6262:6291'>德無常師主善爲師<span class='krp-note'>德非一方以善/爲主乃可師</span>善無常主協</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='6291:6326'>于克一<span class='krp-note'>言以合於能/一爲常德</span>俾萬姓咸曰大哉王言<span class='krp-note'>一德之/言故曰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='6326:6356'><span class='krp-note'>大</span>又曰一哉王心<span class='krp-note'>能一德/則一心</span>克綏先王之禄永底烝民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='6356:6401'>之生<span class='krp-note'>言爲王而令萬姓如此則能保安先王之寵禄長/致衆民所以自生之道是明王之事烝之承反</span>嗚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='6401:6437'>呼七丗之廟可以觀德<span class='krp-note'>天子立七廟有德之王則爲/祖宗其廟不毀故可觀德</span>萬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='6437:6468'>夫之長可以觀政<span class='krp-note'>能整齊萬夫其政/可知長丁丈反</span>后非民罔使民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='6468:6512'>非后罔事<span class='krp-note'>君以使民自尊/民以事君自生</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>后非民罔使民非后/罔事見大禹謨太甲</span>無自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='6512:6532'>廣以狹人匹夫匹婦不獲自盡民主罔與成厥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='6532:6560'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-10a' );" name="005-10a" class="pb">[005-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='6560:6604'>眩厥疾弗瘳<span class='krp-note'>開汝心以沃我心如服藥必瞑眩極其病乃/除欲其出切言以自警瞑莫遍反眩玄遍反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='6604:6642'><span class='krp-note'>徐又呼縣反瞑眩困極/也廖勑留反警音景</span>若跣弗視地厥足用傷<span class='krp-note'>跣必/視地</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='6642:6679'><span class='krp-note'>足乃無害言欲使爲己視聽跣/先典反徐七顯反爲于僞反</span>惟曁乃僚罔不同心以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='6679:6715'>匡乃辟<span class='krp-note'>與汝並官皆當倡率無不同/心以匡正汝君辟必亦反</span>俾率先王迪我髙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='6715:6760'>后以康兆民<span class='krp-note'>言匡正汝君使循先王之/道蹈成湯之蹤以安天下</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>以康兆民武/成以濟兆民</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='6760:6789'>嗚呼欽予時命其惟有終<span class='krp-note'>敬我是命修/其職使有終</span>說復于王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='6789:6817'>曰惟木從繩則正后從諫則聖<span class='krp-note'>言木以繩直/君以諌明</span>后克</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='6817:6849'>聖臣不命其承<span class='krp-note'>君能受諌則臣不待/命其承意而諌之</span>疇敢不祗若王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='6849:6897'>之休命<span class='krp-note'>言王如此誰敢不敬順/王之美命而諌者乎</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>疇敢不祗若王之休命/下篇對揚天子之休命</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='6897:6912'>說命中第十三　商書　孔氏傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='6912:6940'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-10b' );" name="005-10b" class="pb">[005-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='6940:6976'>惟說命緫百官<span class='krp-note'>在冡宰之/任緫音揔</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>緫百官周/官統百官</span>乃進于王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='6976:7006'>曰嗚呼明王奉若天道建邦設都<span class='krp-note'>天有日月北斗/五星二十八宿</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='7006:7059'><span class='krp-note'>皆有尊卑相正之法言明王奉/順此道以立國設都宿音秀</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>奉若天道仲虺之誥奉若/天命○建邦設都武成建</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='7059:7097'><span class='krp-note'>邦啓/土</span>樹后王君公承以大夫師長<span class='krp-note'>言立君臣上下將陳/爲治之本故先舉其</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='7097:7138'><span class='krp-note'>始王于方反長丁丈/反治直史反下同</span>不惟逸豫惟以亂民<span class='krp-note'>不使有位者/逸豫民上言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='7138:7167'><span class='krp-note'>立之主使治/民豫羊慮反</span>惟天聦明惟聖時憲惟臣欽若惟民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='7167:7216'>從乂<span class='krp-note'>憲法也言聖王法天以立教臣敬順/而奉之民以從上爲治從才容反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>惟天聦明惟/聖時憲仲虺</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='7216:7254'><span class='krp-note'>之誥惟天生/聦明時乂</span>惟口起羞惟甲冑起戎<span class='krp-note'>甲鎧胄兠鍪也/言不可輕教令</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='7254:7291'><span class='krp-note'>易用兵冑直又反鎧苦代反兠/丁侯反鍪莫侯反易以䜴反</span>惟衣裳在笥惟干戈省</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='7291:7340'>厥躬<span class='krp-note'>言服不可加非其人兵不可任非其/才笥息嗣反省息井反一本作眚</span>互註<span class='krp-note'>記緇衣兊命/曰惟口起羞</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='7340:7368'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-11a' );" name="005-11a" class="pb">[005-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='7368:7421'><span class='krp-note'>惟甲冑起兵惟衣裳在笥惟干戈省厥躬注云惟口起辱當愼/言語也惟甲冑起兵當愼軍旅之事也惟衣裳在笥當服以爲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='7421:7454'><span class='krp-note'>禮也惟干戈省厥躬/當恕己不尚害人也</span>王惟戒兹允兹克明乃罔不休</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='7454:7496'><span class='krp-note'>言王戒愼此四惟之事/信能明政乃無不美</span>惟治亂在庶官<span class='krp-note'>言所官得人則/治失人則亂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='7496:7526'>官不及私昵惟其能<span class='krp-note'>不加私昵惟能/是官昵女乙反</span>爵罔及惡德</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='7526:7558'>惟其賢<span class='krp-note'>言非賢/不爵</span>慮善以動動惟厥時<span class='krp-note'>非善非時/不可動</span>有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='7558:7588'>其善䘮厥善矜其能䘮厥功<span class='krp-note'>雖天子亦必讓以/得之䘮息浪反</span>惟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='7588:7613'>事事乃其有備有備無患<span class='krp-note'>事事非/一事</span>無啓寵納侮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='7613:7651'><span class='krp-note'>開寵非其人/則納侮之道</span>無恥過作非<span class='krp-note'>恥過誤而丈/之遂成大非</span>惟厥攸居政</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='7651:7688'>事惟醇<span class='krp-note'>其所居行皆如所言則王之/政事醇粹醇音純粹雖遂反</span>黷于祭祀時謂弗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='7688:7726'>欽禮煩則亂事神則難<span class='krp-note'>祭不欲數數則黷黷則不敬事/神禮煩則亂而難行髙宗之祀</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='7726:7754'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-11b' );" name="005-11b" class="pb">[005-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='7754:7794'><span class='krp-note'>特豐數近廟故說因以戒/之黷徒木反數色角反</span>王曰旨哉說乃言惟服<span class='krp-note'>旨美/也美</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='7794:7831'><span class='krp-note'>其所言皆/可服行</span>乃不良于言予罔聞于行<span class='krp-note'>汝若不善於所/言則我無聞於</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='7831:7864'><span class='krp-note'>所行/之事</span>說拜稽首曰非知之艱行之惟艱<span class='krp-note'>言知之易/行之難以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='7864:7897'><span class='krp-note'>勉髙/宗</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>說拜稽首二/又見下篇</span>王忱不艱允恊于先王成德</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='7897:7939'><span class='krp-note'>王心誠不以行之爲難則信/合於先王成德忱市林反</span>惟說不言有厥咎<span class='krp-note'>王能行/善而說</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='7939:7951'><span class='krp-note'>不言則有/其咎罪</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='7951:7966'>說命下第十四　商書　孔氏傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='7966:7996'>王曰來汝說台小子舊學于甘盤<span class='krp-note'>學先王之道甘/盤殷賢臣有道</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='7996:8035'><span class='krp-note'>德者台/音怡</span>旣乃遯于荒野入宅于河<span class='krp-note'>旣學而中廢業遯居/田野河洲也其父欲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='8035:8075'><span class='krp-note'>使髙宗知民之艱苦故/使居民間遯徒頓反</span>自河徂亳曁厥終罔顯<span class='krp-note'>自河往/居亳與</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='8075:8103'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-12a' );" name="005-12a" class="pb">[005-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='8103:8143'><span class='krp-note'>今其終故遂/無顯明之德</span>爾惟訓于朕志<span class='krp-note'>言汝當教訓於/我使我志通逹</span>若作酒醴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='8143:8179'>爾惟麴糵<span class='krp-note'>酒醴須麴糵以成亦言我須/汝以成麴起六反糵魚列反</span>若作和羹爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='8179:8224'>惟鹽梅<span class='krp-note'>鹽鹹梅醋羹須鹹醋以和之羹音庚一音衡鹽/余廉反梅亦作禖醋七故反和如字又胡卧反</span>爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='8224:8256'>交修予罔予棄予惟克邁乃訓<span class='krp-note'>交非一之義邁行/也言我能行汝教</span>說</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='8256:8280'>曰王人求多聞時惟建事學于古訓乃有獲<span class='krp-note'>王/者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='8280:8316'><span class='krp-note'>求多聞以立事學/於古訓乃有所得</span>事不師古以克永丗匪說攸聞<span class='krp-note'>事/不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='8316:8353'><span class='krp-note'>法古訓而以能長丗/非說所聞言無是道</span>惟學遜志務時敏厥修乃來<span class='krp-note'>學/以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='8353:8407'><span class='krp-note'>順志務是敏疾/其德之修乃來</span>互註<span class='krp-note'>記學記夫然故安其學而親其師樂其友/而信其道是以雖離師輔而不反也兊命</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='8407:8447'><span class='krp-note'>曰敬孫務時敏厥修/乃來其此之謂乎</span>允懷于兹道積于厥躬<span class='krp-note'>信懷此學/志則道積</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='8447:8475'><span class='krp-note'>於其/身</span>惟斆學半念終始典于學厥德修罔覺<span class='krp-note'>斆/教</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='8475:8503'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-12b' );" name="005-12b" class="pb">[005-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='8503:8556'><span class='krp-note'>也教然後知所困是學之半終始常念/學則其德之修無能自覺斆戸教反</span>互註<span class='krp-note'>記檀弓古之君子/舉大事必愼其終</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='8556:8609'><span class='krp-note'>始而衆安得不喻焉兊命曰念終始典于學又學記古之王者/建國君民教學爲先兊命曰念终始典于學其此之謂乎又學</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='8609:8660'><span class='krp-note'>然後知不足教然後知困知不足然後能自反也知困然後/能自強也故曰教學相長也兊命曰學學半其此之謂乎</span>監</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='8660:8695'>于先王成憲其永無愆<span class='krp-note'>愆過也視先王成法其長/無過其惟學乎愆起䖍反</span>惟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='8695:8727'>說式克欽承旁招俊乂列于庶位<span class='krp-note'>言王能志學說亦/用能敬承王志廣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='8727:8767'><span class='krp-note'>招俊乂使列衆/官俊本又作畯</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>旁招俊乂太甲/上旁求俊彦</span>王曰嗚呼說四海</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='8767:8802'>之内咸仰朕德時乃風<span class='krp-note'>風教也使天下皆仰我德/是汝教仰如字徐五亮反</span>股</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='8802:8832'>肱惟人良臣惟聖<span class='krp-note'>手足具乃成人/有良臣乃成聖</span>昔先正保衡作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='8832:8871'>我先王<span class='krp-note'>保衡伊尹也作起正長也言先/丗長官之臣長丁丈反/下同</span>乃曰予弗克俾厥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='8871:8904'>后惟堯舜其心愧恥若撻于市<span class='krp-note'>言伊尹不能使其君/如堯舜則恥之若見</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='8904:8932'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-13a' );" name="005-13a" class="pb">[005-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='8932:8969'><span class='krp-note'>撻于市故成其能俾/必爾反撻他逹反</span>一夫不獲則曰時予之辜<span class='krp-note'>伊尹/見一</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='8969:9011'><span class='krp-note'>夫不得其所/則以爲己罪</span>佑我烈祖格于皇天<span class='krp-note'>言以此道左右成湯/功至于天無能及者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='9011:9040'>重言<span class='krp-note'>格于皇天二/本篇君奭</span>爾尚明保予罔俾阿衡專美有商</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='9040:9073'><span class='krp-note'>汝庶幾明安我事則與/伊尹同美阿烏何反</span>惟后非賢不乂惟賢非后不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='9073:9123'>食<span class='krp-note'>言君須賢治賢須/君食治直吏反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>惟后非賢不乂惟賢非后不食太/甲中民非后罔克胥匡以生后非</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='9123:9159'><span class='krp-note'>民罔以/辟四方</span>其爾克紹乃辟于先王永綏民<span class='krp-note'>能繼汝君於/先王長安民</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='9159:9189'><span class='krp-note'>則汝亦有保衡/之功辟必亦反</span>說拜稽首曰敢對揚天子之休命</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='9189:9242'><span class='krp-note'>對荅也荅受美/命而稱揚之</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>說拜稽首二/前篇本篇</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>敢對揚天子之休命上/篇敢不祗若王之休命</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='9242:9258'>髙宗肜日第十五　商書　孔氏傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='9258:9287'>髙宗祭成湯有飛雉升鼎耳而雊<span class='krp-note'>耳不聦之異雊/鳴雊工豆反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='9287:9315'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-13b' );" name="005-13b" class="pb">[005-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='9315:9344'>祖已訓諸王<span class='krp-note'>賢臣也以訓道/諫王已音紀</span>作髙宗肜日髙宗之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='9344:9389'>訓<span class='krp-note'>所以訓也/亡肜音融</span>髙宗肜日<span class='krp-note'>祭之明日又祭殷曰肜周曰繹/繹音亦字書作/爾雅云又祭</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='9389:9425'><span class='krp-note'>也周曰繹商曰/肜夏曰復胙</span>髙宗肜日越有雊雉<span class='krp-note'>於肜日/有雉異</span>祖已曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='9425:9456'>惟先格王正厥事<span class='krp-note'>言至道之王遭變異/正其事而異自消</span>乃訓于王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='9456:9490'>曰惟天監下民典厥義<span class='krp-note'>祖已旣言遂以道訓諫王/言天視下民以義爲常</span>降</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='9490:9519'>年有永有不永非天夭民民中絶命<span class='krp-note'>言天之下年/與民有義者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='9519:9558'><span class='krp-note'>長無義者不長非天欲夭民民自不/修義以致絶命中丁仲反又如字</span>民有不若德不聽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='9558:9596'>罪天旣孚命正厥德<span class='krp-note'>不順德言無義不服罪不改修天/已信命正其德謂有永有不永</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='9596:9641'>乃曰其如台<span class='krp-note'>祖巳恐王未受其言故乃復曰天/道其如我所言台音怡復扶又反</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>其如/台四</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='9641:9670'><span class='krp-note'>湯誓盤庚本/篇西伯戡黎</span>嗚呼王司敬民罔非天㣧典祀無豐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='9670:9698'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-14a' );" name="005-14a" class="pb">[005-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='9698:9747'>于昵<span class='krp-note'>㣧嗣昵近也歎以感王入其言王者主民當敬民事民/事無非天所嗣常也祭祀有常不當特豐於近廟欲王</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='9747:9790'><span class='krp-note'>因異服罪改修之豐芳弓反昵女乙反尸子云不/避逺昵昵近也又乃禮反馬云昵考也謂禰廟也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='9790:9806'>西伯戡黎第十六　商書　孔氏傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='9806:9849'>殷始咎周<span class='krp-note'>咎惡咎其九反馬云/咎周者爲周所咎</span>周人乗黎<span class='krp-note'>乗勝也所以見/惡黎力兮反國</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='9849:9895'><span class='krp-note'>名尚書大/傳作耆</span>祖伊恐<span class='krp-note'>祖已後/賢臣</span>奔告于受<span class='krp-note'>受紂也告相亂帝乙/之子嗣立暴虐無道</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='9895:9941'><span class='krp-note'>受如字傳云受紂也又馬本云受當讀/曰紂或曰受婦人之言故號曰受也</span>作西伯戡黎<span class='krp-note'>戡亦/勝也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='9941:9981'><span class='krp-note'>伯亦作柏戡音堪說文作/云殺也/以此戡訓刺音竹甚反勝詩證反</span>西伯戡黎西伯旣戡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='9981:10016'>黎<span class='krp-note'>近王圻之諸侯在上黨東/北近附近之近圻巨依反</span>祖伊恐奔告于王曰天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='10016:10056'>子天旣訖我殷命<span class='krp-note'>文王率諸侯以事紂貌雖事紂内秉/王心布德行威有將王之意紂不能</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='10056:10109'><span class='krp-note'>制日益強大今又克有黎國迫近王圻似有天助之力故知天/已畢訖殷之王命言殷祚至此而畢將欲化爲周王心于况反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='10109:10137'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-14b' );" name="005-14b" class="pb">[005-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='10137:10178'><span class='krp-note'>下注冝/王者同</span>格人元龜罔敢知吉<span class='krp-note'>至人以人事觀殷大龜/以神靈考之皆無知吉</span>非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='10178:10207'>先王不相我後人惟王淫戲用自絶<span class='krp-note'>非先祖不助/子孫以王淫</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='10207:10238'><span class='krp-note'>過戲怠用自絶於/先王相息亮反</span>故天棄我不有康食不虞天性不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='10238:10286'>迪率典<span class='krp-note'>以紂自絶於先王故天亦棄之宗廟不有安食於天/下而王不度知天性命所在而所行不蹈循常法言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='10286:10313'><span class='krp-note'>多罪度/待洛反</span>今我民罔弗欲䘮曰天曷不降威大命不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='10313:10354'>摯今王其如台<span class='krp-note'>摯至也民無不欲王之亡言天何不下/罪誅之有大命冝王者何以不至王之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='10354:10402'><span class='krp-note'>凶害其如我所言/摯音至本又作贄</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>今我民二盤庚下本篇〇其/如台二盤庚上髙宗肜日</span>王曰嗚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='10402:10437'>呼我生不有命在天<span class='krp-note'>言我生有壽命在天民之/所言豈能害我遂惡之辭</span>祖伊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='10437:10462'>反曰嗚呼乃罪多參在上乃能責命于天<span class='krp-note'>反報/紂也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='10462:10507'><span class='krp-note'>言汝罪惡衆多參列於上天天誅罰汝汝能責/命于天拒天誅乎參七南反馬云參字累在上</span>殷之即䘮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='10507:10535'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-15a' );" name="005-15a" class="pb">[005-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='10535:10573'>指乃功不無戮于爾邦<span class='krp-note'>言殷之就亡指汝功事所致汝/不得無死戮於殷國必將滅亡</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='10573:10600'><span class='krp-note'>立可/待</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>不無戮于爾邦牧/誓其于爾躬有戮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='10600:10614'>微子第十七　商書　孔氏傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='10614:10643'>殷旣錯天命<span class='krp-note'>錯亂也錯七各/反馬云廢也</span>微子作誥父師少師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='10643:10684'><span class='krp-note'>告二師而去/紂少詩照反</span>微子<span class='krp-note'>微圻内國名子爵/爲紂卿士去無道</span>微子若曰父師少</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='10684:10725'>師<span class='krp-note'>父師太師三公箕子也少師孤卿比干微/子以紂距諫知其必亡順其事而言之</span>殷其弗或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='10725:10761'>亂正四方<span class='krp-note'>或有也言殷其不有治正四/方之事將必亡治直吏反</span>我祖底遂陳于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='10761:10791'>上<span class='krp-note'>言湯致遂其功/陳列於上丗</span>我用沈酗于酒用亂敗厥德于下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='10791:10844'><span class='krp-note'>我紂也沈湎酗醟敗亂湯德於後丗沈徐直金反没也酗况具/反以酒爲凶曰酗說文作䣱云酒醟湎面善反醟音詠說文于</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='10844:10882'><span class='krp-note'>命反䣱/酒也</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>沈酗于酒二並本篇/無逸酗于酒德哉</span>殷罔不小大好草竊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='10882:10910'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-15b' );" name="005-15b" class="pb">[005-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='10910:10954'>姦宄<span class='krp-note'>草野竊盗又爲姦宄於/内外好呼報反宄音軌</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>好草竊姦宄舜/典宼賊姦宄</span>卿士師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='10954:10988'>師非度凡有辜罪乃罔恒獲<span class='krp-note'>六卿典士相師效爲非/法度皆有辜罪無秉常</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='10988:11030'><span class='krp-note'>得中者/度如字</span>小民方興相爲敵讎<span class='krp-note'>卿士旣亂而小人各起一/方共爲敵讎言不和同讎</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='11030:11062'><span class='krp-note'>市周/反</span>今殷其淪䘮若渉大水其無津涯<span class='krp-note'>淪没也言/殷將没亡</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='11062:11116'><span class='krp-note'>如渉大水無涯際無所依就淪音倫徐/力允反䘮息浪反涯五佳反又宜佳反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>若渉大水大誥若/渉淵水君奭若渉</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='11116:11150'><span class='krp-note'>大/川</span>殷遂䘮越至于今<span class='krp-note'>言遂䘮亡於是至/於今到不待乆</span>曰父師少</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='11150:11183'>師我其發出狂吾家耄遜于荒<span class='krp-note'>我念殷亡發疾生狂/在家耄亂故欲遯出</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='11183:11226'><span class='krp-note'>於荒野言愁悶出尺遂反耄一又作旄莫報/反注同遯徒悶反徐徒頓反一音都困反</span>今爾無指告</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='11226:11266'>予顛隮若之何其<span class='krp-note'>汝無指意告我殷邦顛隕隮墜如之/何其救之隮子細反玉篇子兮反切</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='11266:11312'><span class='krp-note'>韻祖稽反/隕于敏反</span>父師若曰王子<span class='krp-note'>比干不見明心同省文微子帝/乙元子故曰王子見賢遍反省</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='11312:11340'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-16a' );" name="005-16a" class="pb">[005-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='11340:11372'><span class='krp-note'>所景/反</span>天毒降災荒殷邦方興沈酗于酒<span class='krp-note'>天生紂爲/亂是天毒</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='11372:11406'><span class='krp-note'>下災四方化紂/沈湎不可如何</span>乃罔畏畏咈其耇長舊有位人<span class='krp-note'>言/起</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='11406:11455'><span class='krp-note'>沈湎上不畏天災下不畏賢人違戾耇老之長致仕之賢/不用其教法紂故咈扶勿反耇工口反長丁丈反注同</span>今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='11455:11475'>殷民乃攘竊神祇之犧牷牲用以容將食無災</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='11475:11528'><span class='krp-note'>自來而取曰攘色純曰犧體完曰牷牛羊豕曰牲器實曰用盗/天地宗廟牲用相容行食之無災罪之者言政亂攘如羊反因</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='11528:11567'><span class='krp-note'>來而取曰攘竊馬云往盗曰竊神祇/天曰神地曰祇犧許冝反牷音全</span>降監殷民用乂讎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='11567:11610'>歛召敵讎不怠<span class='krp-note'>下視殷民所用治者皆重賦傷民歛聚怨/讎之道而又亟行暴虐自召敵讎不懈怠</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='11610:11663'><span class='krp-note'>讎如字下同徐云鄭音疇馬本作稠云數也歛力檢反馬鄭力/豔反謂賦歛也徐云鄭力劒反治直吏反亟欺忌反數也又紀</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='11663:11705'><span class='krp-note'>力反本又作極如/字至也懈佳賣反</span>罪合于一多瘠罔詔<span class='krp-note'>言殷民上下有/罪皆合於一法</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='11705:11742'><span class='krp-note'>紂故使民多瘠病而無/詔救之者瘠在益反</span>商今其有災我興受其敗<span class='krp-note'>災/滅</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='11742:11770'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-16b' );" name="005-16b" class="pb">[005-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='11770:11803'><span class='krp-note'>在近我起受其敗言/宗室大臣義不忍去</span>商其淪䘮我罔爲臣僕詔王子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='11803:11846'>出迪<span class='krp-note'>商其没亡我二人無所爲臣僕欲以死諫/紂我教王子出合於道臣僕一本無臣字</span>我舊云刻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='11846:11884'>子王子弗出我乃顛隮<span class='krp-note'>刻病也我乆知子賢言於帝乙/欲立子帝乙不肯病子不得立</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='11884:11932'><span class='krp-note'>則冝爲殷後者子今若不出逃難我殷家宗廟乃隕墜/無主舊云馬云言也刻音克馬云侵刻也難乃旦反</span>自靖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='11932:11971'>人自獻于先王<span class='krp-note'>各自謀行其志人人自獻逹干先/王以不失道靖馬本作清謂潔也</span>我不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='11971:12011'>顧行遯<span class='krp-note'>言將與紂俱死所執各異皆歸於仁明君/子之道出處語黙非一途顧音故徐音鼓</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='12011:12039'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '005-17a' );" name="005-17a" class="pb">[005-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
</p>
<p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='12041:12058'>監本纂圖重言重意互註尚書卷第五</span><br/>
</p>
